title: RY Cooder-Live at The Bottom Line(1974)[FM A][TWR35][CR-Bt]
description:
RY COODER - solo

The Bottom Line
New York City
May 16, 1974

This source is well known as "Traverin' Man" boot. This one was aired on FM in late '70 in Japan. The sound quality is much better(stereo FM!!) than the bootleg, but less incomplete.

Artwork inc.



1. Too Tight Blues No.2
2. FDR in Trinidad
3. The Tattle
4. Crazy About An Automobile
5. I Can Tell By The Way You Smell
6. Kentucky Blues
7. One Meatball(Fade in)
8. How Can A Poor Man Stand Such Times And Live 
9. Preacher
10. Vigilante Man
